creator: WIDO CABS SERVICES
descriptionHtml:
WIDO - Walk In Drive Out is the current all new mobility platform that has been emerged to serve
with transportation services for the commuters who look for safe and secure transits. WIDO Cabs
offers wide range of automobiles that includes motorcycles, auto rickshaws, taxis or cabs that are
convenient to move in. We’ve got professional driver community who can handle our clients well
and give them the best travel experience without any hassles.

We have exceptional mechanism to give the best user experience leaving you under no
confusion to make you choose according to your requirements. Our special features include
surge free prices during any type of weather conditions or any hour in a day. We also provide
expert drivers to hire on whom you can rely for safest rides on their hands. We’ve also got the
wide fleet management system that opens employment opportunities for the people of India.

Have confidence on us and we promise to assist you with excellent transit services from WIDO
Cabs.
Few ride options available on WIDO app includes:
· Bike: Book your ride and travel hassle free, pick and drop from any local location
· Auto: Convenient and cheapest way of transport, no need to wait and haggling for prices
· Micro: Book an AC taxi with lowest price and Safe ride
· Mini: Less Luggage more comfort, travel in our Ac car with affordable prices
· Sedan: Top sedans with experienced friendly drivers
· SUV: Big Family with more luggage, book Spacious Suv Drive in Affordable fares
· Luxury: Book a Luxury car and have a Luxury Ride at Surge free fares
· Outstation: Planning to travel outstation. Book our cab, one way or round trip, with no
surge fares. Sit back and enjoy music, movies and many more
Driver: Your car. Our driver. Hire a professional driver/chauffeur for your car.
